The 2019 Dodge Charger GT is a commanding and sophisticated sedan that blends power, style, and technology. With its sleek black exterior and impressive 3.6L V6 engine, this Charger GT is ready to deliver an exhilarating driving experience.

Key features include:
• Quick Order Package 29H
• 6 Speakers
• Uconnect 4C with 8.4" Display
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Power Driver's Seat
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Rear Back-Up Camera
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto

This Charger GT offers the perfect balance of performance and practicality. The powerful engine and responsive 8-speed automatic transmission provide an engaging and efficient ride, with an impressive 30 MPG on the highway. The well-appointed interior features premium cloth performance seats, a sport steering wheel, and a range of advanced technology and safety features to keep you connected and secure.

Beyond the impressive specs, the Charger GT's bold, muscular styling commands attention on the road. The distinctive grille, sculpted body lines, and 20-inch aluminum wheels give this sedan a confident, aggressive presence that is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Whether you're looking for a daily driver with a thrilling performance edge or a versatile family sedan with plenty of style, the 2019 Dodge Charger GT delivers. With its wealth of features, dynamic driving dynamics, and head-turning good looks, this Charger GT is an exceptional value that is sure to exceed your expectations.

Call us @ 254-213-5876 if you have any questions! We would love to help you!

The spacious interior of this Passat offers ample room for passengers and cargo, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures. With features like dual-zone climate control, a premium audio system, and a power moonroof, you'll enjoy a truly luxurious driving experience.

Visit Ruiz Ranch Motors today to experience firsthand the incredible features and performance of this pre-owned 2019 Volkswagen Passat 2.0T SE R-Line. description:
This 2021 Chevrolet Tahoe High Country is a true standout in the full-size SUV segment. With its commanding presence, premium features, and exceptional capabilities, it's the perfect choice for discerning buyers who demand the very best.

Highlighted features include:

• High Country Deluxe package with adaptive cruise control, panoramic sunroof, and more
• 22" multi-spoke gloss black wheels
• 22" 6-spoke low gloss black wheels with machined accents
• Power-sliding center console with secure storage

Under the hood, this Tahoe is equipped with a potent EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine mated to a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission. The combination of 4WD and Magnetic Ride Control suspension delivers exceptional on-road performance and off-road capability, while the advanced trailering package ensures you can tow with confidence.

Step inside, and you'll be surrounded by luxury. The High Country's perforated leather-appointed seats are both heated and ventilated, ensuring maximum comfort in any weather. The Bose 10-speaker audio system provides a concert-hall experience, while the 15-inch head-up display and Adaptive Cruise Control keep you informed and in control.

Beyond the impressive list of features, this Tahoe High Country also boasts a striking exterior in a bold, Black color. The combination of the premium wheels, chrome accents, and sleek design elements creates a truly commanding presence on the road.

Whether you're looking to transport your family in style, tow your boat or trailer with ease, or simply enjoy the ultimate in full-size SUV luxury, this 2021 Chevrolet Tahoe High Country is the answer. Visit our showroom today to experience it for yourself and see why it's the perfect choice for discerning buyers like you.

description: Discover the Perfect Blend of Style, Efficiency, and Safety with the 2019 Hyundai Elantra Value Edition Experience the refined driving pleasure of the 2019 Hyundai Elantra Value Edition, a vehicle that seamlessly combines style, efficiency, and advanced safety features. This Symphony Silver beauty is designed for those who appreciate the finer details in their daily commute. The 4-cylinder engine paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission ensures a smooth and responsive drive, while the front-wheel-drive system offers excellent traction and control. Safety is paramount in the Elantra, featuring a comprehensive suite of features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Keeping Assist, and Front Collision Mitigation. These systems work together to provide peace of mind on every journey. The heated front seats and leather steering wheel add a touch of luxury, making every drive comfortable and enjoyable. With the Smart Device Integration and Bluetooth Connection, you can effortlessly stay connected and entertained on the go. The Elantra also boasts a sun/moonroof, adding a sense of openness and style to your ride. Its aluminum wheels and performance tires ensure a confident grip on the road, while the back-up camera and keyless entry enhance convenience. Embrace the perfect balance of innovation and practicality with this exceptional mid-size passenger car. Be sure to call or visit Vandergriff Hyundai to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and advanced technology in this stunning 2019 Subaru Legacy 2.5i Limited. With its sleek gray exterior and meticulously crafted interior, this midsize sedan is a true standout on the road.

• High Beam Assist
• LED Steering Responsive Headlights
• Reverse Automatic Braking (RAB)
• Power Moonroof
• Navigation System
• harman/kardon Surround Sound Speaker System
• Radio: Subaru STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Nav System

Powered by a robust 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine and Lineartronic CVT, the Legacy 2.5i Limited delivers an exceptional driving experience with impressive fuel efficiency of 25 MPG in the city and 34 MPG on the highway. The advanced Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system ensures confident handling and control in any driving condition.

Step inside and be captivated by the premium amenities that elevate your daily commute. The perforated leather-trimmed upholstery, heated front and rear seats, and power-adjustable driver's seat provide unparalleled comfort. The Subaru STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Navigation System, complete with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and a suite of connectivity features, keeps you seamlessly connected and entertained.

Safety is paramount in the Legacy 2.5i Limited, with advanced driver-assist technologies like Reverse Automatic Braking, High Beam Assist, and LED Steering Responsive Headlights that help you navigate the road with confidence. The robust safety cell construction and comprehensive airbag system offer additional peace of mind.

This well-equipped Legacy 2.5i Limited is a true testament to Subaru's commitment to craftsmanship, performance, and safety. With its impressive list of features and exceptional value, it's the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands the best. Schedule a test drive today and experience the difference for yourself.

description:
The 2019 Kia Forte FE is a standout vehicle that combines performance, safety, and technology seamlessly. This model is equipped with a robust 2L I-4 DOHC engine that delivers 147 horsepower with a Continuously Variable Transmission CVT, making it both efficient and responsive on the road.

One of the standout features of the Forte FE is its **Smart Device Mirroring** capability. This innovative feature allows you to connect your smartphone to the vehicles infotainment system, offering convenience and enhancing safety by keeping your focus on the road. Gone are the days of fumbling with your device while driving, now, you can control your apps with ease.

Safety is paramount in the 2019 Forte FE, highlighted by its **Forward Collision Mitigation** system. This proactive feature detects potential collisions and prepares the vehicle to help prevent them, giving you peace of mind during your drives. Additionally, the **Rear Camera** provides enhanced visibility of obstacles behind you, acting as an extra set of eyes when reversing.

The **Lane Departure Prevention** system is another impressive safety feature that helps keep you centered in your lane. This system automatically corrects your vehicles position if it detects unintentional lane drifting, ensuring a safer driving experience for you and others on the road.

Furthermore, the **Brake Assist** feature enhances your stopping power during emergency situations. It senses panic braking and applies maximum braking force, which can be crucial in preventing accidents.

On long journeys, the **Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls** feature allows for a more relaxed driving experience, enabling you to maintain a consistent speed without constant pedal work, thereby reducing fatigue.

The **Touchscreen** interface provides intuitive control over various features, making it easy to access information at a glance while driving. The **Variable Valve Timing** technology optimizes engine performance, improving fuel efficiency and reducing emissions.

Finally, the **Driver Attention Monitor** keeps an eye on your alertness, providing warnings if it detects drowsiness or inattention, ensuring your safety on the road.

In summary, the 2019 Kia Forte FE is an impressive vehicle that excels in safety, efficiency, and technology. It’s designed to enhance your driving experience while prioritizing your well-being. Whether you’re commuting or embarking on a road trip, the Forte FE is a reliable companion.

2019 Nissan Sentra S Reliable, Comfortable, and Value-Driven

Discover a compact sedan that delivers everyday practicality with a comfortable ride and excellent efficiency. This 2019 Nissan Sentra S is an ideal choice for commuters, first-time drivers, or anyone looking for a dependable and affordable vehicle without compromising quality.

Performance & Efficiency

Efficient 1.8-liter 4-cylinder engine

Smooth continuously variable transmission (CVT)

Balanced ride quality for city streets and highway cruising

Excellent fuel economy that keeps costs down

Exterior Features

Clean, modern styling with aerodynamic design

Halogen headlights and daytime running lights

Classic sedan profile with easy-access doors

16-inch steel wheels with sleek wheel covers

Interior Comfort & Convenience

Spacious cabin with comfortable cloth seating

Ample headroom and legroom for passengers front and rear

Tilt steering wheel with mounted audio controls

Large trunk with practical cargo space

Technology & Connectivity

7-inch color display audio system

Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming

USB port for easy device connectivity

AM/FM radio with auxiliary input

Safety & Driver Assistance

Nissan Advanced Air Bag System for added protection

Vehicle Dynamic Control with Traction Control System

Rearview monitor for easier backing and parking

Tire pressure monitoring system

Why Youll Love It

Dependable Performance: A smooth, predictable driving experience perfect for daily use

Great Value: Features you want without the high price tag

Comfortable Interior: Roomy seating and thoughtful layout for passengers and cargo

Fuel-Friendly: Efficient performance that helps reduce trips to the pump

This 2019 Nissan Sentra S combines practicality, comfort, and value into one dependable sedan. Its ready to serve your daily driving needs with style and reliability. Contact us today to schedule your test drive!

description:
Thank you for choosing Holler Honda, this Silky Silver 2020 Kia Rio S is a great choice! Check out the following: SILKY SILVER, BLACK, WOVEN CLOTH SEAT TRIM This Rio has the following features: Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
In-car Entertainment
  • Touchscreen - flat out convenient. Say goodbye to the twists and turns of your daily drive...we're talking about buttons and knobs of course! Touchscreen allows you to control certain features with your fingertips, making it easy to use while also providing information at a glance. With touchscreen, your fingerprints will be all over your drive.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
At Holler Honda, all of our vehicles are clearly marked with our haggle-free best price and our sales associates are commission-free. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description:
This 2020 Kia Optima Special Edition, has a Snow White Pearl exterior and an Black interior color. 74,036 miles. Stock Number LG448282. You can connect with us by calling 407-645-1234. No Accidents! SNOW WHITE PEARL, BLACK, LEATHER SEAT TRIM, WHEEL LOCKS, CARPET FLOOR MATS This Optima has the following features: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
To be sure you don't miss out, give us a call at 407-645-1234 and schedule a test drive. We are located at 1970 SR 436 Winter Park FL 32792. We look forward to seeing you soon. FAST & EASY CREDIT APPROVAL!! This vehicle is offered reconditioned and is backed by our market-leading 5-day, 300-mile return policy. If you're not happy with your purchase, just bring it back for a full refund or exchange, plain and simple. Serving all of central Florida, including Orlando, Oviedo, Winter Park, Casselberry, Longwood, Sanford, Winter Garden, Winter Springs, Lake Mary, Maitland, Apopka, and Kissimmee. Victory Auto Store is a family pre-owned car dealership. The store has been operating since 2011. We are located in Stuart, Florida - the Sailfish Capital of the World”.

Victory Auto Group LLC does the business as Victory Auto Store and now has over 100 pre-owned vehicles on the lot. We are proud of the quality used cars we sell and our commitment to meeting our clients' needs. This is apparent in the number of repeat purchases we receive. Whether this is your first purchase with us or one of many, you can count on our devoted sales staff to provide the best possible car buying experience.

Victory Auto Store is your premiere pre-owned automobile dealership. We stock several of the most popular vehicles on the market today. You'll find a large selection of local used cars, trucks, SUVs, vans, and hybrid vehicles. We offer a wide selection of pre-owned Chevrolet, Chrysler, Dodge, Ford, Honda, Jeep, Mitsubishi, Nissan, Pontiac, Acura, Audi, BMW, Lexus, Toyota, Lincoln, Buick, Mercedes, Alfa-Romeo, Huyndai, Kia, Volvo, Porsche, Volkswagen and Subaru cars.

Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance in this stunning 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR. This sleek and sophisticated sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience and take you to new heights.

Boasting a striking blue exterior, this Altima 2.5 SR is equipped with a range of premium features that cater to your every need:

• SR Floor Mats/Trunk Mat/Hideaway Nets

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that seamlessly combines comfort and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of keyless entry, power windows, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls, all while staying connected with the NissanConnect system featuring Apple CarPlay and Android Auto.

Powered by a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder engine paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, this Altima 2.5 SR delivers an impressive fuel economy of 27 mpg in the city and 37 mpg on the highway, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend getaways.

With its sleek design, impressive performance, and comprehensive list of features, this 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR is a true standout in the midsize sedan segment. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the exceptional value and uncompromising quality this Altima has to offer.

description:
The 2020 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S in Pure White is a well-rounded compact sedan that delivers dependable performance, sleek design, and everyday practicality in a timeless package. Wrapped in a bright and clean Pure White finish, this Jetta presents a look thats both crisp and classic a color that highlights the cars smooth lines and refined silhouette while giving it a fresh and modern presence on the road. Whether parked in the driveway or cruising down the highway, the exterior styling of this Jetta strikes a pleasing balance between subtle elegance and sporty appeal.

At the front, the Jetta features a clean, horizontal grille and sharp headlight design that come together for a confident, understated face that feels both contemporary and European-inspired. The bodys well-defined contours flow gracefully from front to rear, and the modest yet thoughtful touches of chrome trim add a touch of sophistication without feeling overdone. The Pure White paint enhances those design cues, reflecting light beautifully and maintaining a crisp, polished appearance in nearly any setting.

Inside the cabin, the 2020 Jetta 1.4T S offers a comfortable and thoughtfully laid-out interior thats designed with both driver and passengers in mind. The seating provides good support and plenty of room for adults up front and in the back, making it practical for daily commuting, weekend road trips, or running errands around town. Controls are logically placed for ease of use, and the ergonomics help make every drive short or long feel relaxed and natural.

The interior materials strike a nice balance of quality and durability, with surfaces that are pleasant to the touch and built to withstand everyday use. The trunk space is generous for the class, providing ample room to carry luggage, groceries, or other gear with ease. Practical storage spaces throughout the cabin add to the convenience, making it easy to stay organized on the go.

Tech features in this Jetta include an intuitive infotainment system that keeps you connected to your favorite music, navigation, and smartphone integration all easily accessed through a responsive touchscreen display. Bluetooth connectivity, USB ports, and other modern conveniences help make life behind the wheel easier and more enjoyable.

Under the hood, the 1.4-liter turbocharged engine offers a lively combination of performance and fuel efficiency. It delivers smooth power for everyday driving and responsive acceleration when you need it, all while helping maintain strong fuel economy figures perfect for commuting or highway cruising. The Jettas handling is stable and composed, with a suspension that absorbs bumps confidently and delivers a comfortable ride quality that makes driving pleasant whether youre on city streets or open roads.

Safety features and thoughtful engineering add peace of mind to every journey, and Volkswagens reputation for solid build quality is evident in the way the Jetta feels responsive and well-made throughout.

Overall, the 2020 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S in Pure White stands out as a dependable and stylish compact sedan that offers a refined driving experience, practical interior space, modern technology, and efficient performance all wrapped in a classic exterior thats both attractive and timeless.

description: Experience the rugged reliability and formidable capabilities of the 2021 Ford Utility Police Interceptor, a versatile SUV designed to meet the demanding needs of law enforcement and emergency services. This used model boasts a sleek black exterior that exudes authority and professionalism, complemented by a comfortable charcoal black interior. With just over 91,400 miles, this vehicle offers a balanced blend of durability and performance. Powered by a robust 3.3-liter V6 engine delivering 285 horsepower and 260 lb-ft of torque, it features a smooth 10-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, ensuring confident handling in a variety of conditions. Whether navigating urban streets or challenging terrains, this SUV is equipped with practical features such as a backup camera, Bluetooth connectivity, and a tow package, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a dependable and capable vehicle. This Police Interceptor is built not only for performance but also for safety and convenience. It includes essential features like knee airbags for front passengers and a comprehensive 4-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) for enhanced control. The vehicle’s auto-locking power door locks add an extra layer of security, while the rear camera system washer ensures clear visibility during reversing maneuvers. Designed with safety at the forefront, this SUV provides peace of mind for drivers and passengers alike, making it a compelling option for professionals and enthusiasts who require both strength and security in their vehicle. 2021 Ford Utility Police Interceptor Safety and Security Features The safety features of this police interceptor prioritize occupant protection and vehicle security. It is equipped with knee airbags for the front passenger, providing additional protection during frontal collisions. The four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) enhances stopping power and stability under emergency braking conditions. Auto-locking power door locks improve security by automatically securing the vehicle once it’s in motion. Additionally, the rear camera system washer ensures the rearview camera remains clean, offering a clear view when reversing, which is vital in high-stakes environments. 2021 Ford Utility Police Interceptor Entertainment and Technology Features The vehicle is equipped with advanced entertainment and connectivity options designed for ease of use and safety. Hands-free phone call integration allows drivers to operate their phones via voice commands, reducing distractions while on the road. The voice-operated radio system provides seamless access to audio controls, keeping driver focus on driving. An auxiliary audio input via USB offers compatibility with various devices, enabling occupants to listen to their preferred music or podcasts effortlessly, enhancing the driving experience even during long shifts. 2021 Ford Utility Police Interceptor Performance Features Performance-wise, the Ford Utility Police Interceptor features full-time four-wheel drive (4WD), ensuring optimal traction and stability regardless of road conditions. This drivetrain configuration allows for confident handling during adverse weather or off-road situations, making it an excellent choice for law enforcement, security, or fleet operations that demand dependable performance in diverse environments. description:
The 2020 Kia Optima LX is an impressive vehicle that combines style, performance, and innovative technology to deliver a remarkable driving experience. This model is powered by the Theta II 2.4L I-4 gasoline direct injection engine, providing a robust 185 horsepower, paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission. Whether youre navigating city streets or cruising down the highway, the Optima LX ensures a responsive and engaging drive.

One of the standout features of the 2020 Kia Optima LX is its **Smart device mirroring**. This functionality allows drivers to seamlessly integrate their smartphones with the vehicles infotainment system, enhancing convenience and safety. With this feature, you can easily access your music, navigation, and other essential apps while keeping your focus on the road ahead.

Safety is paramount in the Optima LX, and the inclusion of **Forward collision mitigation** is a testament to this commitment. The system proactively monitors for potential collisions and takes preventative measures to mitigate the impact. This forward-thinking technology can provide peace of mind for drivers and passengers alike.

Furthermore, the **Front pedestrian impact prevention** feature adds an extra layer of safety. By constantly scanning the road for pedestrians, this system can alert the driver and take corrective actions to avoid potential accidents, making it an essential safety feature for urban driving.

The **Rear camera** enhances visibility and awareness when reversing, providing an extra set of eyes to help avoid obstacles. In addition, the **Lane departure prevention** system ensures that you remain safely within your lane, automatically correcting any unintended movements. This feature is particularly useful on long drives, where fatigue may cause lapses in attention.

The **Brake assist** feature provides an added layer of security by detecting panic braking situations and applying maximum braking power to help avoid accidents. For those who enjoy road trips, the **Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls** makes long-distance driving more comfortable by maintaining a steady speed, reducing driver fatigue.

Comfort is not overlooked in the Optima LX, thanks to the **Power 2-way driver lumbar** support, which allows drivers to adjust their seating for optimal comfort. The **Touchscreen** interface simplifies access to various vehicle functions, making it user-friendly and efficient.

Lastly, the **Rear collision warning** system serves as an invaluable safety feature, alerting drivers to potential hazards behind them. The 2020 Kia Optima LX is designed to prioritize safety, comfort, and driving enjoyment, making it an excellent choice for anyone in the market for a reliable and stylish sedan.

description:
The 2020 Kia Optima LX delivers sleek midsize sedan styling strong efficiency and everyday comfort in a vehicle designed for commuting professional use and long term ownership value. With 80690 miles this Optima reflects consistent real world use while continuing to offer dependable performance supported by proven Kia engineering. Power comes from a responsive four cylinder engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission that provides confident acceleration steady highway cruising and excellent fuel economy. Front wheel drive supports predictable handling balanced road manners and a composed ride across city streets highways and longer trips.

Inside the Optima LX offers a spacious thoughtfully designed cabin focused on comfort usability and clean modern design. Premium cloth seating a power adjustable driver seat and a well organized dashboard layout create a welcoming driving environment. The interior provides generous headroom and legroom for both front and rear passengers while wide door openings enhance ease of entry and exit. Split folding rear seats expand trunk capacity for luggage groceries work items or travel gear. Soft touch materials refined trim accents and practical storage solutions throughout the cabin support everyday driving needs.

Technology in the 2020 Optima LX is intuitive driver focused and built for convenience. A large color touchscreen anchors the Kia infotainment system with Apple CarPlay Android Auto Bluetooth and voice command capability. Steering wheel mounted controls keep audio phone and cruise functions easily accessible while maintaining focus on the road. Multiple USB ports keyless entry push button start and a clear driver information display add everyday ease for commuting and travel.

Safety remains a strong advantage of the Optima lineup. Advanced safety features include forward collision avoidance lane keeping assist lane departure warning driver attention monitoring and a rearview camera. Stability control traction control antilock braking and a comprehensive airbag system support confidence across a wide range of driving conditions. The low center of gravity predictable steering response and excellent outward visibility further enhance driver confidence during daily use.

The exterior of the 2020 Kia Optima LX features sleek aerodynamic body lines LED lighting alloy wheels and a bold modern front fascia. The refined styling enhances efficiency while delivering a confident professional road presence suitable for both personal and business use. Its combination of fuel efficiency interior space modern safety technology and proven reliability has made the Optima a trusted choice in the midsize sedan segment. For drivers seeking a value driven sedan with comfort technology strong efficiency and everyday practicality the 2020 Kia Optima LX remains an excellent option.

Why Buy from Jackie Cooper Nissan
Every used vehicle on our lot goes through a strenuous 150 point inspection before it is ever offered for sale because quality and safety are part of our heritage. Our factory trained technicians examine all major systems including engine transmission brakes suspension tires and electrical components to ensure each vehicle meets our high standards for performance and reliability. We also inspect for signs of prior damage mechanical issues and cosmetic wear inside and out. If something does not meet our strict criteria it is either repaired or replaced before the vehicle reaches the lot. This careful process reflects our commitment to your peace of mind because you deserve a vehicle you can count on.

    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description: This used 2020 Kia Forte LXS offers an exceptional blend of style, efficiency, and modern technology, making it a compelling choice for drivers seeking a reliable sedan. Sporting an elegant Aurora Black Pearl exterior complemented by a sleek black interior, this vehicle has traveled 94,914 miles and remains a versatile option with its spacious four-door design and seating for five. Powered by a 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine with a smooth CVT transmission, it delivers an impressive 147 horsepower and 132 lb-ft of torque, ensuring responsive performance on every drive. Its fuel economy stands out with 29 mpg in the city and 40 mpg on the highway, making it an economical choice for daily commuting and longer trips alike. This used Forte LXS is equipped with key features like Apple CarPlay, a backup camera, Bluetooth connectivity, collision warning, and lane keep assist, all designed to enhance safety and convenience for the modern driver. This used Kia Forte LXS combines advanced driving assistance with user-friendly technology, providing a secure and connected experience. The vehicle’s safety suite includes four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) and automatic locking power door locks, emphasizing security and control during every journey. Its suite of entertainment and tech features ensures drivers stay connected and entertained, with an 8-inch touchscreen infotainment display serving as the hub for multimedia functions. Hands-free phone call integration, voice-operated, allows effortless communication while on the move. The in-car system supports connected apps through an app marketplace, offering additional functionality, while electronic messaging assistance—read and voice-operated—keeps communication seamless and safe. Auxiliary inputs, including USB and iPod/iPhone connectivity, ensure compatibility with various devices for a personalized audio experience. 2020 Kia Forte Safety and Security Features This used Kia Forte prioritizes safety with essential features such as four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS), which enhances braking performance and stability. Additionally, the vehicle is equipped with auto-locking power door locks, providing added security by automatically locking doors when driving, helping to protect occupants and valuables. 2020 Kia Forte Entertainment and Technology Features On the entertainment front, this used Forte features an 8-inch touchscreen display that serves as the central control for radio, smartphone integration, and connected apps. Hands-free phone call capabilities are voice-operated, allowing drivers to stay connected without distraction. The system supports auxiliary audio inputs via USB and iPod/iPhone, catering to various media preferences, while electronic messaging assistance, both read and voice-operated, ensures safe and convenient communication on the go. Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency in this stunning 2020 Kia Forte LXS. With its sleek black exterior and a host of premium features, this compact sedan is the ideal choice for the modern driver seeking a sophisticated and well-equipped ride. • Aurora Black exterior • Carpet floor mats Packed with an impressive array of amenities, this Forte LXS offers an exceptional driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone and access your favorite apps on the go. The rear-view camera provides added peace of mind when maneuvering in tight spaces, while the steering wheel-mounted audio controls keep your music and calls at your fingertips. Boasting an EPA-estimated 29 MPG in the city and an impressive 40 MPG on the highway, this Forte LXS delivers exceptional fuel efficiency, making it an economical choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures. The 2.0L 4-cylinder engine and CVT transmission provide a smooth and responsive driving experience, ensuring you can navigate the roads with confidence. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, featuring comfortable woven cloth seats, a front center armrest, and a split-folding rear seat for added versatility. The power windows, remote keyless entry, and air conditioning add to the overall comfort and convenience of this Forte LXS. Safety is a top priority, and this vehicle is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, electronic stability control, and a tire pressure monitoring system work together to provide you and your passengers with the utmost protection. With its exceptional combination of style, technology, efficiency, and safety, this 2020 Kia Forte LXS is the perfect choice for the discerning driver. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the quality and value this Forte has to offer.

description:
INFO ABOUT THIS VEHICLE: Our Stormy Sea 2020 Hyundai Sonata SE has 59,239 miles with Black interior color. Stock Number HHLH061561U Important Package Information Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience in the 2020 Hyundai Elantra SE. This sleek and well-equipped sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Boasting a striking Blue exterior, the Elantra SE is more than just a pretty face. Under the hood, a 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission delivers an impressive 30 city/40 highway MPG, ensuring you'll spend less time at the pump and more time on the open road.

• Reversible Cargo Tray
• Center Console Tray
• First Aid Kit

The Elantra SE is packed with features that cater to your every need. Dual-zone automatic climate control keeps you and your passengers comfortable, while the AM/FM audio system with 6 speakers provides the perfect soundtrack for your commute. Steering wheel-mounted audio controls and remote keyless entry add to the convenience, and the rear-view camera makes parking a breeze.

Safety is a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, dual front and side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control providing you with peace of mind. The Lane Departure Warning System helps you stay centered in your lane, while the Brake Assist feature ensures you can stop quickly when needed.

The well-appointed interior of the Elantra SE is designed with your comfort in mind. Premium Cloth Seat Trim and a Front Center Armrest create a relaxing environment, while the Split Folding Rear Seat allows you to adapt the cabin to your needs. The Tilt and Telescoping Steering Wheel and Trip Computer further enhance the driving experience.

This 2020 Hyundai Elantra SE is an exceptional value, combining stylish design, impressive efficiency, and a wealth of desirable features. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional sedan.

We surveyed hundreds of our past clients to find out how they want to purchase a vehicle and we have listened. We designed a fast, fair, and simple process to save you time and eliminate the need for the back-and-forth that out clients have told us they dislike (or even hate!). You will find that we do things very different than you may have experienced in the past and have come to expect with other dealers. We call this: Simple Price, Simple Process! Our Simple Price will be the same regardless of where you see our vehicle. We do extensive research to know the market. We utilize the same reliable tools you may use (Kelley Blue Book, Edmunds, Craigslist, etc), as well as some others (sales data, auction data, shopping our competition), to offer every vehicle at a very fair and aggressive market-based purchase price. We use this process for every vehicle, new and used, to eliminate the need for back-and-forth negotiations. Our clients have told us that this develops trust and the confidence to purchase. This saves our clients time (in some cases even hours or days of negotiation) and provides the 100% transparent experience our clients tell us they want.

From your first contact with us (call, text, email or store visit), to the time you drive away in your new vehicle, our Simple Price and Simple Process will save you time. You will work with only one person from beginning to end. Your professional Sales Manager will present the vehicle you have selected and offer to share any others that are similar. Once you have selected the vehicle you would like to own, there is no need to negotiate. In addition, Toyota Sunnyvale’s Simple Process has been streamlined by eliminating the wait for the “Finance Department,” saving you an hour (or two) to see a finance manager. Your Sales Manager invests an additional 30+ hours per year of training to professionally offer your protection options. They already know you and what will provide the maximum benefits during your ownership so they will tailor your experience to the items best suited to you.

Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and efficiency in this 2018 Ford Fusion SE. With its sleek white exterior and a host of impressive features, this Fusion is poised to exceed your expectations and deliver an exceptional driving experience.

• FORD COMMERCIAL GRAPHICS (up to 90 square feet)

Powered by a 2.5L iVCT engine and a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Fusion SE delivers an impressive 21 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, making it a practical and fuel-efficient choice. The vehicle's well-equipped interior, including features like the SYNC Communications & Entertainment System, power driver's seat, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls, ensures a comfortable and connected journey.

Beyond the essentials, this Fusion SE offers a wealth of desirable amenities. Enjoy the convenience of the Rear Parking Camera, the security of the Emergency Communication System, and the added confidence of Electronic Stability Control and Traction Control. The Fusion's sleek and modern design is complemented by the 17" Sparkle Silver Painted Aluminum wheels, adding a touch of style to your daily commute.

Whether you're navigating the city streets or embarking on a road trip, this 2018 Ford Fusion SE is ready to take you there in comfort and style. With its well-rounded performance, impressive fuel efficiency, and comprehensive list of features, this Fusion is a compelling choice for the discerning driver.

We invite you to experience the Fusion SE for yourself. Visit our showroom and let our knowledgeable sales team guide you through a test drive. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Fusion's capabilities and excited about the prospect of making it your next vehicle.

description:
Introducing the sleek and stylish 2018 Hyundai ELANTRA Sport, a true standout in the world of sedans. This top-of-the-line model is packed with features that will elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful 1.6L Turbo GDI engine, delivering a thrilling 201 horsepower and 195 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a 7-speed Dual Clutch Transmission, this car offers smooth and responsive handling, perfect for those who crave a little extra excitement on the road.

Step inside the ELANTRA Sport and you'll be greeted with a spacious and luxurious interior. The leather-wrapped sport seats provide both comfort and support, while the dual-zone automatic temperature control ensures everyone stays cool and comfortable on even the longest drives.

But the ELANTRA Sport is more than just a pretty face. It's also loaded with advanced technology, including a 7-inch display audio system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone for hands-free calling, messaging, and music streaming.

Safety is always a top priority, which is why the ELANTRA Sport comes equipped with a suite of advanced safety features, such as Blind Spot Detection with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert and Lane Change Assist, to help you stay aware of your surroundings at all times.

Don't miss your chance to experience the 2018 Hyundai ELANTRA Sport for yourself. With its sleek design, powerful performance, and cutting-edge technology, this sedan is truly in a league of its own. Visit your nearest Hyundai dealership today and see why the ELANTRA Sport is the ultimate choice for those who demand nothing but the best.

description:
Introducing the 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT, the ultimate combination of style, performance, and technology. This stunning sedan boasts a sleek and modern exterior design, complete with a bold front grille and elegant curves. But it's what's under the hood that truly sets the Malibu LT apart.

Equipped with a powerful 1.5L turbocharged engine, this car delivers an impressive 160 horsepower and 184 lb-ft of torque. The smooth and responsive 6-speed automatic transmission ensures a seamless driving experience, while the advanced suspension system provides a comfortable ride on any road.

Step inside and experience the luxurious and spacious interior of the Malibu LT. With available leather-appointed seats, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel, every drive will feel like a first-class experience. And with the latest technology features, including an 8-inch touchscreen display, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, and a built-in 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot, staying connected on the go has never been easier.

But the 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT isn't just about style and comfort, it's also packed with advanced safety features to give you peace of mind on the road. From the available Lane Keep Assist and Forward Collision Alert to the Rear Vision Camera and Teen Driver technology, this car has you covered from every angle.

Experience the 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT for yourself and see why it's the perfect combination of form and function. Visit your nearest dealership and schedule a test drive today. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional sedan.

description:
Discover the exceptional value and performance of this 2018 Honda Civic EX. With its sleek exterior, advanced technology, and impressive fuel efficiency, this Civic is the perfect blend of style, comfort, and capability.

• Carfax One Owner
• Cruise Control
• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth
• 16 CARFAX SERVICE HISTORY RECORDS
• 8 Speakers
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic Temperature Control
• Power Windows
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• ABS Brakes
• Dual Front Airbags
• Power Moonroof
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

Powered by a 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V i-VTEC engine and a CVT transmission, this Civic delivers an exceptional driving experience with an EPA-estimated 31 MPG in the city and 40 MPG on the highway. The sleek, aerodynamic design not only looks great but also contributes to its impressive fuel efficiency, allowing you to spend less time at the pump and more time enjoying the open road.

Inside, the Civic EX offers a spacious and well-appointed cabin, with features like a 180-Watt AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM Audio System, Bluetooth connectivity, and a Rearview Camera to keep you connected and aware of your surroundings. The Cloth Seat Trim provides a comfortable and durable seating experience, while the Power Moonroof adds an extra touch of sophistication.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Civic EX featuring a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including Dual Front Airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and an Emergency Communication System. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected.

This 2018 Honda Civic EX is a true testament to the brand's commitment to quality, reliability, and innovation. With its exceptional features, impressive performance, and unbeatable value, it's the perfect choice for the discerning driver. Visit our showroom today to experience the Civic EX for yourself and discover why it's one of the most sought-after compact cars on the market.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and efficiency in this 2018 Honda Accord Sport. This exceptional sedan boasts a striking gray exterior and a well-appointed interior that will elevate your driving experience.

• Must See
• Hard to Find
• USB Port
• Steering Wheel Audio Controls
• Premium Stereo
• Power Windows/Locks/Mirrors
• Power Driver's Seat

Under the hood, the Accord Sport is powered by a 1.5T I4 DOHC 16V Turbocharged VTEC engine, delivering an impressive 29 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway. This responsive powertrain, paired with a CVT transmission and front-wheel drive, provides a smooth and engaging driving experience. Whether navigating city streets or cruising the open road, this Accord Sport will exceed your expectations.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin. Enjoy the convenience of features like the 8-speaker premium audio system, dual-zone automatic climate control, and the intuitive infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The power driver's seat and leather-wrapped steering wheel add a touch of sophistication, while the split-folding rear seat offers versatility for your cargo needs.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Accord Sport boasting a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assist technologies. From the Blind Spot Monitoring system to the Rear View Camera, you can have peace of mind knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

This 2018 Honda Accord Sport is a true standout in its class, blending style, performance, and cutting-edge features. With a list price of just $13,330, it represents an exceptional value that is sure to impress. Don't miss your chance to experience the Accord Sport for yourself.     Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience with this 2018 Nissan Sentra S. This compact sedan offers a remarkable combination of features that make it an exceptional choice for the modern driver.

• Carpeted Floor Mats w/Trunk Mat
• Body Colored Splash Guards (4 Piece)
• Rear USB Ports

Powered by a 1.8L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine and paired with a CVT with Xtronic transmission, this Sentra delivers an impressive 27 city/35 highway MPG, ensuring you'll spend less time at the pump and more time on the open road. The front-wheel-drive configuration provides a smooth and responsive driving experience, while the traction control system enhances stability and control in various road conditions.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that prioritizes both comfort and technology. The Cloth Seat Trim offers a refined and inviting atmosphere, while the Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls and Rear USB Ports allow you to stay connected and entertained on your journeys. The Tilt and Telescoping Steering Wheel, along with the Illuminated Entry and Outside Temperature Display, further enhance the driver-centric design.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control ensuring your peace of mind on the road. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear provides added confidence when maneuvering in tight spaces, while the Delay-Off Headlights and Fully Automatic Headlights ensure optimal visibility in any lighting conditions.

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2018 Nissan Sentra S is the perfect companion. With its impressive fuel efficiency, comprehensive feature set, and unwavering commitment to safety, this sedan is poised to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and experience the Sentra for yourself – we're confident you'll be impressed.

description:
Discover exceptional value and dependable performance with the 2018 Hyundai Elantra SEL Gray FWD, available now at Toyota of Fort Walton Beach. This stylish sedan features a fuel-efficient 2.0L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission with Shiftronic, delivering an impressive 28 city/37 highway MPG for confident daily driving and long road trips.

The sleek Gray exterior is complemented by 16-inch alloy wheels that combine style and durability, while the cloth seat trim ensures comfort throughout every journey. Safety is paramount with standard features such as ABS brakes, Electronic Stability Control, dual front impact and side airbags, knee airbags, and a rear exterior parking camera for enhanced visibility.

Enjoy modern tech with the AM/FM HD radio with SiriusXM, integrated Apple CarPlay and Android Auto for seamless smartphone connectivity, and a premium sound system featuring 6 speakers. Convenience features include power windows and mirrors, remote keyless entry, speed control, and a trip computer to keep you informed on every drive.

Additional highlights include heated door mirrors, automatic headlights with delay-off feature, front bucket seats with center armrest, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and tilt and telescoping steering wheel for personalized driving comfort.

At Toyota of Fort Walton Beach, we offer transparent, fair pricing backed by thorough market analysis extending up to a 500-mile radius, ensuring you receive the best deal based on the vehicles history and condition. After your test drive, ask your product specialist for a detailed research market analysis. If you find a comparable vehicle for less, were happy to discuss the differences or match the price on a like vehicle in our area.

The 2018 Hyundai Elantra SEL comes with an outstanding pedigree, earning accolades such as the 2018 KBB.com 10 Best Sedans Under $25,000, 10 Coolest New Cars Under $20,000, 5-Year Cost to Own Awards, and recognition as one of the 10 Most Awarded Brands.

Explore the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and advanced safety with the 2018 Hyundai Elantra SEL Gray today at Toyota of Fort Walton Beach your trusted dealership for quality pre-owned vehicles in Florida.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and advanced technology in this 2018 Hyundai Elantra SEL. With its sleek silver exterior and well-appointed interior, this compact sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Elantra SEL is designed to cater to your every need. Key highlights include:

• Apple CarPlay & Android Auto integration
• Reversible cargo tray for versatile storage
• Rear bumper applique for added protection
• Carpeted floor mats for a premium touch
• Mud guards to keep your vehicle looking its best

Under the hood, the Elantra SEL is powered by a 2.0L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission with Shiftronic. This efficient powertrain delivers an exceptional 28 MPG in the city and 37 MPG on the highway, making it an ideal choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that prioritizes both style and functionality. The Elantra SEL comes equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced technologies, including a display audio system, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and a rearview camera for added convenience and safety.

Comfort and convenience are also at the forefront, with features like air conditioning, power windows, and remote keyless entry. The split-folding rear seats and ample cargo space ensure you can easily accommodate your lifestyle needs.

Safety is paramount in the Elantra SEL, with a robust suite of features that include antilock brakes, electronic stability control, and a comprehensive airbag system to provide you and your passengers with the utmost protection.

This 2018 Hyundai Elantra SEL represents an exceptional value proposition, with a list price of just $9,500. Experience the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and technology in this well-equipped compact sedan. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this Elantra for a test drive. Let us demonstrate how it can elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations.

    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    In-car Entertainment
    • Touchscreen - flat out convenient. Say goodbye to the twists and turns of your daily drive...we're talking about buttons and knobs of course! Touchscreen allows you to control certain features with your fingertips, making it easy to use while also providing information at a glance. With touchscreen, your fingerprints will be all over your drive.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and efficiency in this stunning 2018 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR. With its sleek, sporty design and a wealth of advanced features, this Altima is poised to elevate your driving experience.

Elevate your commute with the Altima's impressive list of premium amenities, including:

• Interior Lighting Package
• Illuminated Kick Plates
• External Ground Lighting
• Body Color Body Side Moldings
• Sport Carpeted Floor Mats/Trunk Mat (5-Piece)
• Splash Guards
• Sub Floor Cargo Organizer
• Rear USB Port

This Altima 2.5 SR is powered by a potent 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, delivering an exceptional balance of power and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 26 city/37 highway MPG, you can enjoy the thrill of the open road while keeping your fuel costs in check.

Slip behind the wheel and experience the Altima's refined interior, featuring premium cloth seating, a leather-wrapped shift knob, and a host of intuitive technology. The 6-speaker audio system with AM/FM/CD/MP3 capabilities ensures your favorite tunes will accompany you on every journey.

Safety is paramount in the Altima, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and electronic stability control ensuring your peace of mind on the road. The four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering provide a responsive and confident driving experience, no matter the conditions.

Whether you're commuting to the office or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2018 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR is ready to elevate your driving experience. Visit our showroom today and discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology that this Altima has to offer.

Discover sophistication and power intertwined in this 2018 Cadillac CTS 3.6L Premium Sedan, enveloped in an elegant Silver Moonlight Metallic exterior with a plush Light Platinum and Jet Black accented interior. The rear-wheel-drive sedan hosts a spirited 3.6L V6 engine paired seamlessly with an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering a smooth and confident driving experience.

Inside this luxury chariot, comfort meets technology. The cabin is artfully crafted with genuine wood accents, leather seating surfaces, and tri-zone climate control, ensuring both driver and passengers enjoy a cozy, yet opulent ride. The power-adjustable, heated, and ventilated front seats provide unparalleled comfort for long journeys, while the rear passengers appreciate the heated outboard seating.

For tech enthusiasts, the Cadillac User Experience with embedded navigation elevates your commute, while the Bose Centerpoint Surround Sound 13-Speaker System elevates your auditory senses. Connectivity is seamless with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, and features like the color head-up display and remote keyless entry make every drive effortless.

Safety is paramount with the Driver Awareness Package including Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist, and Rear Cross Traffic Alert. The seamless Automatic Parking Assist takes the stress out of urban driving, allowing you to navigate tight spots with grace. Magnetic Ride Control and adaptive suspension ensure a velvety ride over any terrain.

Stay serene under the UltraView power sunroof, opening your world to panoramic skies, and embrace a premium lifestyle with automatic high-beam headlights, rain-sensing wipers, and stylish 18" alloy wheels completing the picture of refined elegance.

Experience the Cadillac difference at Newton Nissan South where transparent pricing and a hassle-free approach await. This impeccable CTS won't last long, visit today and let us elevate your drive to new heights!

description: Our 2018 Mercedes-Benz C 300 4MATIC, Sedan in stunning Black helps you enjoy every drive with comfort and performance. Motivated by a TurboCharged 2.0 Liter 4 Cylinder generating 241hp coupled to a 9 Speed Automatic transmission to send you to 60mph in 5.8 seconds. This All Wheel Drive C-Class sedan features up to 30mpg on the highway, responsive handling, a smooth, quiet ride, and attractive styling highlighted by a power sunroof, LED daytime running lights, and eye-catching alloy wheels. Once inside our C 300, you will be impressed with the stylish trim and unsurpassed attention to detail. Settle into the power front sports seats with driver memory and admire the amenities such as a multi-function steering wheel, keyless ignition, and dual-zone automatic climate control. The full-color infotainment system also features Bluetooth,, dual USB inputs, and high-fidelity audio for your entertainment needs. Our Mercedes-Benz surrounds you with safety technology to help keep you out of harm's way. You will find forward collision warning with active brake intervention, a driver-drowsiness monitor, a back-up camera, rain-sensing wipers, advanced airbags, ABS, and stability/traction control for your peace of mind. You will love every drive in our C 300 sedan. Save this Page and Call for Availability. With its spacious interior and comfortable seating, the 2018 Toyota Corolla is designed to provide the utmost comfort for you and your passengers. The sleek exterior design is not only eye-catching but also aerodynamic, ensuring a smooth and efficient ride.

But don't let its compact size fool you, the 2018 Toyota Corolla is packed with advanced features such as a backup camera, Bluetooth connectivity, and a state-of-the-art audio system. Plus, with its excellent fuel efficiency, you'll save time and money at the pump.

Safety is always a top priority, and the 2018 Toyota Corolla has you covered with its advanced airbag system, anti-lock brakes, and stability control. You can drive with peace of mind knowing that you and your passengers are protected at all times.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fantastic 2018 Toyota Corolla. Visit our dealership today to take a test drive and experience its impressive performance and features for yourself. Hurry, this beauty won't last long!

description:
This 2018 Chevrolet Cruze LS, has a Mosaic Black Metallic exterior and an Jet Black interior color. 108,903 miles. Stock Number GS260380B. You can connect with us by calling (585) 359-2200. Preferred Equipment Group 1SB
  • 6-Speed Automatic Transmission
In-car Entertainment
  • Touchscreen - flat out convenient. Say goodbye to the twists and turns of your daily drive...we're talking about buttons and knobs of course! Touchscreen allows you to control certain features with your fingertips, making it easy to use while also providing information at a glance. With touchscreen, your fingerprints will be all over your drive.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

You'll feel at home in our XE Premium when you slip inside one of its perfectly formed power front seats with driver-side memory. Before you set off, cue up your favorite tunes on our Jaguar's easy-to-use full-color Touch Pro infotainment system, offering Bluetooth,, USB inputs, and concert-quality Meridian audio. Then, get ready to be pampered by amenities, including a multi-function steering wheel, keyless ignition, HomeLink, auto-dimming rearview mirrors, and dual-zone automatic climate control. Safety is one of Jaguar's top concerns, so you'll find a backup camera, rain-sensing wipers, traction/stability control, ABS, and advanced airbags on hand for your peace of mind. You deserve to reward yourself with our phenomenal XE Premium sedan! Save this Page and Call for Availability.     Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description: This used 2018 Chevrolet Cruze LT offers a compelling blend of efficiency, technology, and style, making it an excellent choice for drivers seeking reliable transportation with modern amenities. With just under 40,000 miles, this sedan features a vibrant red exterior complemented by a refined brown interior, providing a stylish yet practical ride. Powered by a 1.4-liter turbocharged four-cylinder engine, it delivers an impressive 153 horsepower and 177 lb-ft of torque, ensuring spirited acceleration while maintaining excellent fuel efficiency—29 mpg city and 40 mpg highway. Equipped with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel drive, this Cruze is designed for everyday comfort and confident handling. Its suite of advanced features includes Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth connectivity, a backup camera, blind spot monitor, satellite radio readiness, and a WiFi hotspot, offering seamless integration and entertainment on the go. Whether commuting or weekend cruising, this used Chevrolet Cruze LT combines practicality with modern technology to elevate your driving experience. Designed to prioritize safety without compromising comfort, this used Chevrolet Cruze LT is packed with essential security features. It includes a rear seat reminder to ensure passenger safety, dual front knee airbags, and four-wheel ABS for confident stopping power. Power door locks feature anti-lockout technology, providing added convenience and security, while a programmable safety key offers customized access control. These safety features work together to create a secure environment, giving drivers peace of mind whether navigating city streets or highway routes in this dependable sedan. 2018 Chevrolet Cruze Safety and Security Features This used Cruze LT is equipped with a comprehensive safety package that emphasizes protection and security. It features a rear seat reminder to alert drivers to check the back seats before exiting, dual front knee airbags for additional impact protection, and four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) to prevent wheel lockup during emergency stops. Power door locks include anti-lockout functionality, ensuring ease of access for authorized users. The vehicle also comes with a programmable safety key, allowing owners to set personalized access controls, enhancing overall security and peace of mind. 2018 Chevrolet Cruze Entertainment and Technology Features This used Chevrolet Cruze LT offers a host of entertainment and technological amenities designed to keep drivers connected and engaged. The centerpiece is a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system that supports voice-operated radio functions, providing easy access to music and navigation. It includes internet radio apps such as Pandora and Stitcher, enabling streaming of favorite stations and podcasts. The vehicle features a total of six speakers, delivering clear audio throughout the cabin. Additional connectivity options include auxiliary audio inputs via USB and compatibility with iPod/iPhone devices, ensuring versatile media playback. Electronic messaging assistance, both read function and voice-operated, keeps communication accessible and safe while on the move. 2018 Chevrolet Cruze Performance Features Performance in this used Chevrolet Cruze LT is enhanced by a range of intelligent features focused on efficiency and responsiveness. Notably, the vehicle is equipped with auto start/stop technology, which automatically shuts down and restarts the engine to help save fuel and reduce emissions during idle periods. This feature complements the turbocharged 1.4-liter engine, providing a balanced mix of power and economy. The combination of this performance feature and the vehicle’s lightweight design ensures a smooth, efficient ride without sacrificing driving enjoyment. Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and practicality with this 2018 Chevrolet Cruze LT. This compact sedan offers an exceptional driving experience, packed with a host of advanced features that cater to your every need. Highlighted by its striking Blue exterior, the Cruze LT boasts a sleek and modern design that is sure to turn heads. Under the hood, a 1.4L 4-Cylinder Turbo DOHC CVVT engine, paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 29 MPG in the city and 40 MPG on the highway. • Chevrolet MyLink with 7" Touch-Screen • SiriusXM Satellite Radio • Rear Parking Camera • Heated Door Mirrors • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto • Cloth Seat Trim This Cruze LT is equipped with a host of advanced safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and a Rear Parking Camera, ensuring your peace of mind on the road. Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that offers ample space and comfort. The Cruze LT's Cloth Seat Trim, Front Center Armrest, and Split Folding Rear Seat provide a cozy and versatile cabin, perfect for your daily commute or weekend adventures. With a list price of just $14,995, this 2018 Chevrolet Cruze LT represents an exceptional value proposition in the compact sedan segment. Backed by Chevrolet's reputation for reliability and innovation, this Cruze LT is a smart choice for the discerning buyer seeking a well-equipped, fuel-efficient, and stylish vehicle. We invite you to experience the Cruze LT for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the perfect blend of performance, technology, and value that this remarkable compact sedan has to offer.
