description: **CALL OR TEXT ALEJANDRO (ALEX) @ 440-749-1370 FOR A PERSONALIZED WALK AROUND VIDEO OR TO SET UP A TEST DRIVE AND ANSWER ANY QUESTIONS YOU MAY HAVE!** Experience style, comfort, and advanced safety in this Black 2018 Mazda Mazda6 Touring Sedan. Powered by a SKYACTIV-G 2.5L I4 engine with a smooth 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission and front-wheel drive, this Mazda6 is built for an engaging yet efficient drive. Inside, enjoy luxury touches like heated leatherette seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob, and dual-zone automatic climate control. The 8-inch Mazda Connect infotainment system supports both Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, while Bluetooth and HD Radio keep you connected and entertained. Safety is top-notch with adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, blind spot monitoring with rear cross traffic alert, front automatic emergency braking, and a rearview camera. Enjoy added convenience with keyless entry and push-button start, rain-sensing wipers, and a power sunroof. Aluminum alloy wheels, LED headlights, and chrome trim complete the premium look. This Mazda6 Touring is ready for your test drive today!

Introducing the 2018 Mazda Mazda6 Signature – the ultimate combination of luxury and performance.

Step into the spacious and refined interior, featuring premium Nappa leather-trimmed seats, wood trim accents, and a 360-degree view monitor for enhanced driving confidence. The 8-inch MAZDA CONNECT™ infotainment system provides seamless connectivity and entertainment on every journey.

Experience the 2018 Mazda Mazda6 Signature for yourself and elevate your driving experience to new heights. Visit our showroom today and take a test drive. With its sleek design, advanced technology, and impressive performance, this sedan is sure to turn heads and leave a lasting impression. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own the ultimate luxury sedan.

This 2018 Hyundai Elantra SEL, has a Scarlet Red exterior and an Gray interior color. 121,797 miles. Stock Number AC7626A. You can connect with us by calling . OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Option Group 01
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. Blind spot warning alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear so you know if you're about to make an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with confidence and safety with blind spot warning.
    • Rear collision warning - It has your back. This system uses sensors to monitor the area behind you. If it senses an impending crash, it alerts you so you can take steps to prevent a collision or reduce the severity of it. Rear collision warning, a second set off eyes watching over you.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    OPTION GROUP 01, SCARLET RED, GRAY, CLOTH SEAT TRIM All of our vehicles comes with Miracle Pro Plus. Ask Sales for details. At Miracle Buick GMC of Kutztown, we're here to Serve you! Our staff is 100% dedicated to customer satisfaction and we understand that you need clear, transparent information throughout the car buying process. With our live market pricing philosophy, we offer the right cars at the right price, and the transparency to back it up!

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in this stunning 2018 Mazda Mazda3 Grand Touring. With its sleek black exterior and well-appointed interior, this vehicle is a true head-turner that will elevate your driving experience.

• 3 Month/4,000 Mile Comprehensive Warranty
• Triton Certified Classic Vehicle
• Bose 9 Speaker Surround Sound Audio System
• Heads-Up Display
• Power Moonroof
• Heated Front Seats
• Perforated Leather Seat Trim
• 18" Dark Silver Finish Alloy Wheels
• Rear View Camera

Under the hood, this Mazda3 Grand Touring is powered by a SKYACTIV® 2.5L 4-cylinder engine, delivering an impressive 27 city/36 highway MPG. The 6-speed automatic transmission provides smooth, responsive shifting, ensuring a dynamic and efficient driving experience.

Stepping inside, you'll be surrounded by a wealth of premium features designed to elevate your daily commute. The Bose 9-speaker surround sound system and Heads-Up Display keep you connected and entertained, while the heated leather-trimmed seats and power moonroof add an extra touch of luxury.

This Mazda3 Grand Touring is more than just a stylish ride – it's a certified Triton Classic Vehicle, meaning it has undergone a rigorous inspection and reconditioning process to ensure exceptional quality and reliability. With a comprehensive 3-month/4,000-mile warranty, you can drive with confidence, knowing your investment is protected.

Experience the perfect balance of sophistication, performance, and technology in this 2018 Mazda Mazda3 Grand Touring. Schedule a test drive today and discover why this vehicle is the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2018 Hyundai Elantra Sport. Boasting a sleek black exterior and a powerful 1.6L Turbo GDI 4-Cylinder engine, this vehicle is designed to deliver an exhilarating performance on the road.

• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Power moonroof
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• High-Intensity Discharge Headlights
• Speed control
• Apple CarPlay & Android Auto
• Heated Front Sport Seats
• Split folding rear seat
• 18" x 7.5" Alloy Wheels

The Elantra Sport's interior is equally impressive, with premium features that cater to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of the auto-dimming mirror with HomeLink, the comfort of the carpeted floor mats, and the versatility of the reversible cargo tray. This vehicle is a true testament to Hyundai's commitment to quality and innovation.

Under the hood, the Elantra Sport's 7-Speed Automatic transmission and Front-Wheel Drive system provide a smooth and responsive driving experience, while the impressive fuel efficiency of 26 city and 33 highway MPG ensures you can enjoy the open road without constantly stopping for gas.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and electronic stability control ensuring your peace of mind on every journey.

Whether you're commuting to work or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2018 Hyundai Elantra Sport is the perfect companion. With its exceptional performance, premium features, and unbeatable value, it's no wonder this vehicle is in high demand.

***After 122 years in business, we know how to do our homework. We are confident that after researching over 20,000 websites that this beautiful ride is priced extremely competitively based on its value proposition. Come in and we will prove it to you! It will be the best decision you ever made! Hurry before your neighbor gets here to claim this enormous value!

Used 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT Sedan 4D for sale in Pottstown, PADiscover this used 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT Sedan 4D, a sleek and efficient choice for drivers seeking a reliable yet stylish vehicle. With a striking black exterior and matching black interior, this Malibu combines modern aesthetics with practicality. Its 1.5-liter turbocharged four-cylinder engine delivers 160 horsepower and 184 lb-ft of torque, ensuring responsive performance whether you're commuting or cruising on the highway. Equipped with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission and front-wheel drive, this sedan offers a comfortable ride and impressive fuel economy of 27 mpg city and 36 mpg highway. With 92,668 miles on the odometer, this used Malibu provides dependable performance, ideal for daily use and long trips. Stay connected and entertained with features like Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, satellite radio readiness, and a WiFi hotspot, integrated into an intuitive infotainment system with a 7-inch touchscreen display. Convenience features include keyless entry, push-start ignition, and a backup camera to assist parking and maneuvering. This used Chevrolet Malibu combines modern technology, efficient performance, and a stylish appearance, making it a great value and reliable choice for today s driver.This used 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT offers a comprehensive suite of safety and security features to ensure peace of mind. It includes a rear seat reminder to alert you to check the back seats before exiting, helping prevent accidental oversight. Dual front knee airbags and a four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) enhance occupant safety during collisions or emergency stops. Auto-locking power door locks provide added security, and a programmable safety key allows customizable access restrictions. These features work together to create a safe environment for driver and passengers, emphasizing Chevrolet s commitment to safety in this dependable used sedan.2018 Chevrolet Malibu Safety and Security FeaturesThe safety and security of this used Malibu are further supported by its safety measures. The rear seat reminder helps prevent leaving children or pets unattended. Dual front knee airbags and four-wheel ABS ensure protection during sudden stops or impacts. Auto-locking power door locks and a programmable safety key add security and control. These features collectively offer owners peace of mind and confidence behind the wheel.2018 Chevrolet Malibu Entertainment and Technology FeaturesEntertainment and technology are prioritized in this used Malibu. It features a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system with a touch screen display, providing easy access to radio, navigation, and connectivity options. The vehicle is equipped with six speakers delivering clear sound. It supports multiple internet radio apps, including Pandora, Stitcher, and TuneIn, for streaming music and news. Electronic messaging assistance is both voice-operated and includes a read function, allowing safer communication while driving. Bluetooth connectivity and satellite radio readiness further enhance entertainment options, making every trip more enjoyable.2018 Chevrolet Malibu Performance FeaturesThis used Malibu s performance is highlighted by its auto start/stop system, which improves fuel efficiency by shutting down the engine during idle periods and restarting it smoothly when needed. This feature helps enhance gas mileage and reduces emissions, making it an eco-friendly option. The turbocharged engine, efficient transmission, and start/stop technology combine to deliver a balanced mix of power and economy for everyday driving needs.* Easy Financing!* Buy 100 % Online!

description:
Experience the perfect balance of style, technology, and efficiency with this 2018 Nissan Sentra SV. Boasting a sleek black exterior and a well-appointed interior, this compact sedan is ready to elevate your daily driving experience.

Highlighted features include:
• Premium Package (P01) with power moonroof, navigation, and advanced connectivity
• Protection Package with rear bumper protector, trunk protector, and body side moldings
• Carpeted floor mats with trunk mat

Beyond these premium upgrades, the Sentra SV offers a host of desirable amenities, such as:
• Dual-zone automatic climate control
• Steering wheel-mounted audio controls
• Rear-view camera with dynamic guidelines
• Keyless entry and push-button start

Under the hood, the 1.8L 4-cylinder engine delivers a remarkable balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 29 mpg in the city and 37 mpg on the highway. The Xtronic CVT transmission provides smooth, responsive acceleration, making this Sentra a joy to drive.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like anti-lock brakes, stability and traction control, and a comprehensive airbag system to help protect you and your passengers.

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2018 Nissan Sentra SV is the perfect companion. Its blend of style, technology, and efficiency make it a standout in the compact sedan segment.

We invite you to experience the Sentra SV for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of driving this exceptional vehicle. We're confident you'll be impressed by its capabilities and confident it will exceed your expectations.

description: The 2018 Nissan Altima stands as a testament to practical engineering and everyday reliability, offering drivers a seamless blend of comfort, efficiency, and contemporary design. With 102,318 miles on the odometer, this sedan has been thoughtfully maintained and reflects Nissan’s reputation for longevity and dependable performance. Cloaked in a sleek black exterior, the Altima makes an understated yet modern impression on city streets and highways alike. Its streamlined profile and signature front grille exhibit a sense of purpose that speaks to both style-conscious drivers and those who appreciate functional design. Under the hood, the Altima is powered by a responsive 2.5-liter 4-cylinder engine mated to an automatic transmission. This combination delivers dependable acceleration as well as commendable fuel efficiency, making it well-suited for daily commutes or longer road trips. Drivers will appreciate the smooth transitions between gears and the balanced ride quality provided by Nissan’s thoughtfully engineered suspension system. The powertrain is not only robust but also tuned for quiet operation, contributing to a refined driving experience regardless of speed or road conditions. Stepping inside, occupants are greeted by an interior designed for both comfort and convenience. Though specific details about trim features are not specified here, the Altima’s reputation is built on thoughtful ergonomics, supportive seating, and intuitive controls that make every journey pleasant. The sedan’s spacious cabin ensures ample legroom for both front and rear passengers, while wide-opening doors provide easy access for all seats. Whether commuting solo or traveling with family or friends, occupants are likely to find the environment accommodating for extended drives. Attention to safety and technology is evident throughout the Altima's design. Nissan has equipped this model year with a suite of standard safety features intended to inspire confidence behind the wheel. From advanced airbag systems to anti-lock brakes and stability control, essential protective measures come standard. Many models in this generation also include convenient connectivity options such as Bluetooth integration and available touchscreen interfaces—ideal for those who value staying connected on the go without distraction. On the road, the Altima delivers a composed yet engaging driving experience. The steering provides reassuring feedback while remaining light enough for effortless maneuvering in tight spaces or busy traffic. Road noise is effectively muted thanks to comprehensive insulation measures throughout the cabin, allowing conversations or audio entertainment to remain clear at all times. Whether navigating urban environments or cruising on open highways, this sedan remains poised and responsive. For buyers seeking substance over flash in their daily transportation, this 2018 Nissan Altima presents itself as an appealing choice. Its combination of proven mechanical reliability, efficient performance, and enduring style ensures it remains relevant in today’s competitive sedan market. description: This used 2018 Mercedes-Benz E 300 sedan exemplifies luxury and performance, offering a refined driving experience wrapped in an elegant Polar White exterior complemented by a sophisticated Macchiato Beige and Black interior. With 136,540 miles on the odometer, this vehicle remains a compelling choice for those seeking a premium sedan that balances power and comfort. Equipped with a turbocharged 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine generating 241 horsepower and 273 lb-ft of torque, it delivers spirited acceleration while maintaining impressive fuel efficiency of up to 30 mpg highway. The rear-wheel-drive layout ensures a dynamic driving feel, enhanced by features like Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth connectivity, a backup camera, navigation, and a sunroof, making every journey both convenient and enjoyable. The sedan's sleek four-door design seats five comfortably and is loaded with modern amenities, including memory seats, push start, satellite radio readiness, fog lights, collision warning, and more, all in a used but well-maintained condition. This used Mercedes-Benz E-Class offers a suite of advanced safety and security features designed to protect occupants and provide peace of mind. It includes knee airbags for the driver, active head restraints in the front, and four-wheel ABS to enhance braking performance. Additional safety systems such as emergency braking preparation, cornering brake control, auto-locking power door locks, brake drying, and an electronic parking brake with auto-off ensure confidence behind the wheel. These features combine to create a formidable safety net, making this used E 300 a dependable choice for daily driving or long-distance travel. 2018 Mercedes-Benz E-Class Safety and Security Features The safety and security features of this used E 300 are comprehensive, beginning with knee airbags for the driver and active head restraints for both front seats, which help mitigate injury risks in a collision. Four-wheel ABS provides reliable braking control, while emergency braking preparation and cornering brake control enhance safety during sudden stops or sharp turns. The vehicle also comes with auto-locking power door locks, brake drying to improve braking in wet conditions, and an electronic parking brake with auto-off functionality, all contributing to a secure driving environment. 2018 Mercedes-Benz E-Class Entertainment and Technology Features Equipped with a 12.3-inch infotainment screen, this used E 300 offers an intuitive interface for navigation and media control. Voice-operated hands-free phone call integration and radio, including HD radio, ensure seamless connectivity and entertainment options. The system features eight speakers delivering clear sound quality, real-time traffic data to assist in route planning, and auxiliary audio inputs via USB and iPod/iPhone compatibility. These technological amenities enhance the driving experience, providing convenience and entertainment at every turn. 2018 Mercedes-Benz E-Class Performance Features Under the hood, this used Mercedes-Benz E 300 boasts performance features designed to optimize ride quality and handling. Auto start/stop technology helps improve fuel economy by shutting down the engine during stops. The driver-adjustable suspension allows for personalized ride comfort, while the self-leveling suspension maintains optimal ride height regardless of load. Additionally, a tuned sport suspension offers enhanced agility for spirited driving, ensuring this used sedan delivers a dynamic and comfortable performance in all conditions.

description: The 2020 Jeep Grand Cherokee SRT is a high-performance SUV that combines rugged capability with luxurious refinement. Powered by a formidable 6.4-liter V8 engine delivering 475 horsepower, this Grand Cherokee SRT commands the road with impressive acceleration and all-wheel-drive traction. Its aggressive exterior styling is complemented by a sport-tuned suspension and distinctive SRT badging, giving it a bold presence. The interior offers a premium driving experience with supple leather seats, a user-friendly Uconnect infotainment system, and advanced technology to enhance both comfort and performance. The vehicle is also equipped with a Wi-Fi hotspot, allowing passengers to stay connected on the go, whether commuting in the city or venturing out on a road trip.----Inside the cabin, modern tech meets safety and convenience. Adaptive Cruise Control helps maintain a safe distance from vehicles ahead, while the advanced Collision Warning system adds an extra layer of protection during daily drives. Navigation is built into the infotainment system and delivers turn-by-turn directions on a large touchscreen display, ensuring drivers stay on the right path. Premium audio provides a rich sound experience, ideal for enjoying music or podcasts with exceptional clarity. The 2020 Grand Cherokee SRT showcases Jeep's dedication to performance and sophistication, making it an excellent option for those who want SUV practicality combined with muscle-car performance and luxury comfort. Whether you're towing gear, navigating tough terrain, or cruising the open road, this vehicle offers power, precision, and peace of mind.

description: This 2018 Chevrolet Impala in Summit White is the LS trim, offering a sleek and stylish exterior that complements its powerful performance. Under the hood, it features a robust 3.6L V6 engine generating 305 horsepower at 6800 rpm, paired with an automatic transmission for seamless driving. The front-wheel-drive system ensures excellent handling and stability on the road. The interior is trimmed in luxurious Jet Black/Dark Titanium leather, providing both comfort and sophistication. With seating for up to five passengers, this sedan is designed for both driver and passenger convenience. Fuel efficiency is impressive with an EPA rating of 18 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, making this vehicle practical for daily commutes or long trips. Convenience features abound, including keyless entry and start, Bluetooth connectivity for hands-free calling, and a back-up camera for added safety when reversing. This model comes equipped with modern technology like smart device integration and a Wi-Fi hotspot so you can stay connected on the go. Enjoy music through the AM/FM stereo with MP3 capability while utilizing steering wheel audio controls for ease of use. Safety features enhance peace of mind with multiple airbags throughout the cabin, traction control, ABS brakes, and child safety locks to keep your loved ones secure. Additional practical touches include adjustable steering wheel options, power windows and door locks, cruise control for comfortable highway driving, and rear defrost to tackle those chilly mornings. A range of premium comforts such as bucket seats along with floor mats add to the overall appeal of this Impala. This well-rounded vehicle blends style functionality seamlessly making it a solid choice for anyone looking to enjoy a driving experience enriched by numerous thoughtful options.

description:
Discover the exceptional value and versatility of this 2004 Chevrolet Impala Base. With its well-equipped interior, efficient powertrain, and timeless design, this Impala is the perfect blend of practicality and style.

• Local Trade
• Preferred Equipment Group 1SB
• Electronic Cruise Control w/Set & Resume Speed
• 3 Outboard Passenger Assist Handles
• Carpeted Front & Rear Floormats
• Deluxe Covered Illuminated Vanity Visor Mirrors
• Trunk Cargo Convenience Net

Slip behind the wheel of this Impala and experience the comfort of the front sport cloth 60/40 split-bench seat, complete with a 6-way power driver's seat and manual recline for both the driver and front passenger. The front center armrest with storage and 60/40 split-folding rear seat with center armrest and cup holders offer exceptional versatility, allowing you to customize the cabin to suit your needs.

Enjoy the convenience of electronic cruise control, which allows you to maintain a consistent speed on the highway, reducing driver fatigue and improving fuel efficiency. The 3 outboard passenger assist handles and deluxe covered illuminated vanity visor mirrors add an extra touch of refinement, while the carpeted front and rear floormats and trunk cargo convenience net help keep your Impala tidy and organized.

Under the hood, the 3.4L V6 SFI engine and 4-speed automatic transmission with overdrive provide a smooth and efficient driving experience, delivering an impressive 21 mpg in the city and 32 mpg on the highway. With its front-wheel-drive configuration, the Impala offers confident handling and responsive performance, making it a practical and enjoyable daily driver.

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, this 2004 Chevrolet Impala Base is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and efficiency for yourself. We're conveniently located at 222 40th St. S. in Fargo and easy to reach at (701) 282-8425. You can also browse current inventory and offers anytime at CorwinToyota.com. Pricing and availability are subject to dealer verification.

Discover the Versatility and Efficiency of the 2017 Ford Focus SE

Introducing the 2017 Ford Focus SE - a compact car that combines dynamic performance, exceptional fuel economy, and a wealth of premium features. This well-equipped model offers the perfect blend of style, technology, and practicality, making it an ideal choice for the modern driver.

• 3 Point Leather-Wrapped Heated Steering Wheel
• Heated Front Seats
• Heated Mirrors
• SYNC Communications & Entertainment System
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Air Conditioning
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls

Powered by a 2.0L 4-Cylinder DGI Flex Fuel Turbocharged DOHC engine paired with a 6-Speed Automatic Transmission, the Focus SE delivers an impressive 26 MPG in the city and 38 MPG on the highway. This efficient powertrain not only saves you money at the pump but also provides a responsive and engaging driving experience.

The Focus SE's sleek and modern design is further enhanced by the Ruby Red Metallic Tinted Clearcoat exterior, which exudes a refined and sophisticated look. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin featuring comfortable cloth front bucket seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a host of advanced technologies to keep you connected and entertained.

Safety is also a top priority in the Focus SE, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, electronic stability control, and a rear-view camera to help you navigate with confidence.

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, the 2017 Ford Focus SE is the perfect companion. Its versatility, efficiency, and impressive list of features make it a standout choice in the compact car segment.

We invite you to experience the Focus SE for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let our knowledgeable sales team demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can enhance your driving experience. With its blend of performance, technology, and value, the Focus SE is sure to exceed your expectations.

Discover the exceptional 2017 Nissan Sentra SR, a sleek and versatile sedan that seamlessly blends style, technology, and performance. This captivating vehicle is the perfect companion for the discerning driver seeking a dynamic and refined driving experience.

Boasting a striking white exterior, the Sentra SR commands attention with its bold and sporty design. Equipped with the Driver's Assist Package, this sedan offers a suite of advanced features that elevate your driving experience:

• Nissan Connect with Navigation and Mobile Apps
• Blind Spot Warning and Rear Cross Traffic Alert
• Carpeted Floor Mats with Trunk Mat

Beyond these impressive capabilities, the Sentra SR is packed with a wealth of premium amenities that cater to your every need. Indulge in the comfort of heated front seats, the convenience of a power-adjustable driver's seat, and the sophistication of leather-appointed seating. Seamlessly connect your smartphone with the intuitive infotainment system, which includes a 5.8-inch color touchscreen, SiriusXM Radio, and voice recognition for audio and navigation.

Beneath the sleek exterior, the Sentra SR is powered by a robust 1.8-liter 4-cylinder engine that delivers an exceptional balance of efficiency and performance. With an impressive 37 MPG on the highway, this sedan ensures you can enjoy the open road without compromising your fuel savings. The Xtronic CVT with Xtronic transmission provides a smooth and responsive driving experience, while the front-wheel-drive configuration ensures confident handling in a variety of road conditions.

Safety is paramount in the Sentra SR, which is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Enjoy the peace of mind of Electronic Stability Control, 4-Wheel Disc Brakes with ABS, and a suite of airbags to protect you and your passengers. The Rear View Camera and Blind Spot Warning system further enhance your awareness on the road, allowing you to navigate with confidence.

Experience the exceptional value and refined driving dynamics of the 2017 Nissan Sentra SR. This remarkable sedan is a testament to Nissan's commitment to engineering excellence and customer satisfaction. Visit our showroom today to take this captivating vehicle for a test drive and discover the true joy of ownership.

In terms of safety, the Legacy has you covered with its advanced safety features including Subaru's EyeSight Driver Assist Technology, which includes pre-collision braking, adaptive cruise control, and lane departure warning. With these features, you can feel confident and secure on every journey.

With its sleek design, powerful engine, advanced technology, and top-of-the-line safety features, the 2017 Subaru Legacy 2.5i Premium is the perfect choice for anyone looking for a reliable and stylish sedan. This Altima 2.5 SR is the perfect combination of style, performance, and value. With its sleek exterior, robust powertrain, and comprehensive list of features, it's the ideal choice for the discerning driver who wants it all. Welcome to Champaign-Urbana Auto Park – Your Trusted Source for Quality Pre-Owned Vehicles
At Champaign-Urbana Auto Park, we’re proud to be your #1 destination for high-quality, pre-owned vehicles. With years of experience serving the community, we’re dedicated to offering only the best in pre-owned cars, trucks, and SUVs—ensuring you drive away with a vehicle you can count on.
-Thanks to our strong relationships in the dealer community, we’re able to access a wide variety of lease returns and new car trades, allowing us to offer exceptional values on the vehicles you want. This means we can pass along huge savings to our customers, helping you find the perfect car at an unbeatable price.
We Offer Financing & Accept Trade-Ins!

-Whether you're working with a budget or just need some flexibility, we offer financing options that can help you get into the car you’ve been dreaming of. Plus, if you're thinking of trading in your current vehicle, we’ll offer you a competitive trade-in value to make the process even easier. If you're looking to sell your car outright, we're actively looking to buy quality vehicles and will make you a great offer!
-From the moment you step through our doors, you’ll experience a hassle-free, customer-first car-buying experience. Our friendly, knowledgeable sales team is here to assist, and we’ll work with you to make sure you find the right vehicle at the right price.
Have questions, want to learn more about our financing or trade-in process, or ready to find your next car? Call us at (217) 367-5044 or stop by in person. We can’t wait to help you drive away in a car you’ll love!

This meticulously crafted sedan is designed to impress with its striking presence and exhilarating performance, making it the perfect choice for those who demand more from their daily drive. With a mileage of 96,663 miles, this Fusion Titanium has been expertly maintained to ensure it delivers the reliability and performance you expect from a Ford. Under the hood, you'll find the heart of this beast: the robust EcoBoost 2.0L Turbo I4 engine. This powerhouse churns out an impressive 245 horsepower and 275 lb-ft of torque, offering the perfect balance of power and efficiency. Paired with a 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, this Fusion provides a smooth, responsive ride that adapts effortlessly to your driving style, whether you're navigating city streets or cruising down the highway. Step inside, and you'll be enveloped in a world of luxury and comfort. The interior features exquisite leather seating that adds a touch of elegance, making every journey a first-class experience. The attention to detail is evident in every stitch, ensuring that you and your passengers travel in supreme comfort. The Fusion Titanium is not just about comfort, it’s about creating an environment where you can truly enjoy the ride. The 2017 Ford Fusion Titanium stands out in its class, having earned prestigious accolades such as Edmunds's Top Recommended Sedans and being a Kelley Blue Book's Best Buy: Midsize Car Finalist. These awards are a testament to its exceptional design, performance, and value, giving you the confidence that you're investing in a vehicle that has been recognized for its excellence. But the Fusion Titanium isn’t just about accolades, it’s about the experience. Imagine the thrill of commanding its turbocharged power as you merge effortlessly onto the freeway, or the satisfaction of knowing that your vehicle is as efficient as it is powerful. The EcoBoost engine delivers not only impressive performance but also remarkable fuel efficiency, ensuring that you spend less time at the pump and more time enjoying the open road. Safety and technology are at the forefront of the Fusion Titanium’s design. It’s equipped with advanced features that work seamlessly to enhance your driving experience. From intuitive controls to cutting-edge infotainment systems, every journey is as connected as it is enjoyable. Whether you're streaming your favorite tunes or navigating to your next destination, this Fusion is designed to keep you in command and entertained. In conclusion, the 2017 Ford Fusion Titanium is more than just a car, it's a statement of style, power, and innovation. With its award-winning pedigree, luxurious interior, and turbocharged performance, it’s a vehicle that invites you to experience the road like never before. Don’t miss the opportunity to own a sedan that combines beauty, brains, and brawn in perfect harmony. Visit us today and take this exceptional Fusion Titanium for a test drive, and discover why it’s the midsize car that everyone is talking about. Your next adventure awaits!

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional sedan that promises to deliver an unparalleled driving experience. description:
Introducing the 2017 Chevrolet Sonic LT Auto - the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology. This compact car is designed to make your daily commute a breeze while turning heads on the road.

The Sonic LT Auto boasts a sleek and modern exterior, featuring a bold front grille and striking LED headlights. Step inside and experience the spacious and comfortable cabin, with ample legroom and premium cloth seating. The LT trim also includes a leather-wrapped steering wheel for added luxury.

But the real star of the show is under the hood. The 2017 Sonic LT Auto comes equipped with a 1.4L turbocharged engine, delivering an impressive 138 horsepower and 148 lb-ft of torque. Coupled with a 6-speed automatic transmission, this car offers a smooth and responsive ride.

But the Sonic LT Auto isn't just about performance, it's also loaded with advanced technology. Stay connected on the go with Chevrolet's MyLink infotainment system, complete with a 7-inch color touchscreen and smartphone integration. And with available features like a rearview camera and 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot, you'll have everything you need for a seamless driving experience.

Safety is always a top priority, and the 2017 Sonic LT Auto doesn't disappoint. This car comes equipped with 10 standard airbags and available features like Lane Departure Warning and Forward Collision Alert to keep you and your passengers protected.

Don't miss your chance to own this versatile and stylish 2017 Chevrolet Sonic LT Auto. Visit our showroom or schedule a test drive today and experience the difference for yourself. With its impressive features and affordable price point, this car is sure to exceed all your expectations. Don't wait, drive home in a 2017 Sonic LT Auto today!

description: The 2017 Chevrolet Cruze LT Auto 4-Door Sedan is a compact car that blends efficiency, comfort, and modern features into a practical package suited for daily commuting, long drives, and small families alike. As a mid-level trim in the Cruze lineup, the LT model adds a number of convenience and tech upgrades over the base version, making it a well-rounded choice for drivers who want value without sacrificing comfort or amenities. Visually, the Cruze maintains a clean and contemporary look with Chevrolet’s characteristic twin-port grille, swept-back headlights, and smooth body lines that give it a slightly more premium appearance than many other vehicles in its class. Its compact size makes parking and maneuvering in tight spaces easy, while the overall design remains understated yet polished. Step inside, and the Cruze LT offers a cabin that feels thoughtfully arranged and comfortable. Seating for five is supported by well-cushioned seats that are ideal for daily use or longer road trips, and the amount of space in both front and rear seats is respectable for a compact sedan. Materials throughout the interior lean toward the practical side, but there are plenty of soft-touch areas and an attention to detail that elevates the overall feel above basic economy cars. For cargo, the trunk is generous, making it easy to carry groceries, luggage, or gear for a weekend adventure. Under the hood, the 2017 Cruze LT Auto typically comes with a four-cylinder engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission that prioritizes fuel efficiency and ease of operation. Acceleration is competent for everyday driving, providing enough power for highway merging and overtaking without feeling strained. One of the Cruze’s strong suits is its fuel economy, it’s engineered to deliver strong mileage, which can be especially appealing for commuters and drivers looking to reduce fuel costs over time. Technology and convenience features on the LT include keyless entry, a touchscreen infotainment system with Chevrolet’s MyLink interface, Bluetooth connectivity, and available smartphone integration, making it easy to stay connected and entertained on the go. Cruise control, power accessories, and automatic climate control add to the comfort and ease of use. Standard safety features like multiple airbags, stability control, and anti-lock brakes help provide confidence behind the wheel. Overall, the 2017 Chevrolet Cruze LT Auto 4-Door Sedan is a solid, sensible compact car that balances practicality, comfort, and modern conveniences. It’s particularly appealing for those who want reliable transportation with thoughtful features and good fuel economy in a stylish, easy-to-drive package.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in this stunning 2017 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR. With its sleek blue exterior, this Altima commands attention on the road, turning heads wherever it goes. Under the hood, the powerful 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with the smooth-shifting CVT with Xtronic transmission delivers an impressive 26 city/37 highway MPG, making it an exceptional choice for the daily commute or weekend getaways.

This Altima 2.5 SR comes equipped with a host of premium features to elevate your driving experience, including:

• Sport Carpeted Floor Mats/Trunk Mat (5-Piece)
• Body Color Body Side Moldings
• Splash Guards
• Chrome Bumper Protector

In addition, you'll enjoy the convenience of a rearview camera, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and a premium audio system with AM/FM/CD/MP3 playback. The spacious interior, with its comfortable cloth seating and ample cargo space, ensures that every journey is both enjoyable and practical.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and this Altima 2.5 SR delivers with features like dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and electronic stability control. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected.

The Altima 2.5 SR's nimble handling and responsive steering make it a joy to drive, whether navigating city streets or winding country roads. The four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering provide a smooth, controlled ride, while the 18-inch sport aluminum alloy wheels add a touch of sportiness to the overall design.

This 2017 Nissan Altima 2.5 SR is a remarkable vehicle that offers the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology. With its impressive fuel efficiency, comprehensive safety features, and premium amenities, it's the ideal choice for the discerning driver. Visit our showroom today to experience the Altima 2.5 SR for yourself and discover why it should be your next automotive investment.

description: The 2017 Ford Fusion SE AWD 4-Door Sedan is a well-balanced midsize car that blends comfort, style, and capability into a package that appeals to daily commuters and families alike. With its all-wheel-drive system, the Fusion SE stands out in its class by offering increased confidence and stability on a variety of road surfaces, especially in wet or slippery conditions. It’s a sedan that feels substantial and refined without being overly complex or expensive to own. From the exterior, the 2017 Fusion SE strikes a modern and athletic pose. Its sleek lines, sculpted body panels, and distinctive front grille give it a look that feels more upscale than its price tag suggests. The design is cohesive and aerodynamic, helping to improve fuel efficiency and reduce wind noise at highway speeds. The four-door layout is classic and functional, yet the overall styling feels fresh and contemporary, appealing to buyers who want a sedan that stands out without screaming for attention. Under the hood, the Fusion SE typically comes equipped with a responsive four-cylinder engine that strikes a pleasing balance between performance and fuel economy. The engine delivers smooth power for merging on highways and passing slower traffic, while also remaining composed and efficient during everyday city driving. The addition of all-wheel drive enhances traction and control, making the car more planted through rain, light snow, and unsettled pavement. The transmission shifts predictably and smoothly, aiding in a relaxed driving experience. Inside, the cabin of the Fusion SE is thoughtfully designed with quality materials, comfortable seating, and an intuitive layout. Front seats are supportive and well-shaped for longer drives, while rear passengers enjoy respectable legroom and headroom for a midsize sedan. The overall interior ambiance feels more upscale than expected for the trim level, with tactile surfaces and a straightforward dashboard that avoids clutter. Technology features in the SE trim are practical and user-friendly. The infotainment system offers a touchscreen interface with smartphone integration, audio streaming, and voice controls that make it easy to stay connected without distraction. Standard convenience features like keyless entry, Bluetooth connectivity, and a rearview camera help round out the package without unnecessary complexity. Safety is a strong point for the 2017 Fusion SE, with a range of features designed to help keep occupants secure. The structure feels solid and many drivers appreciate the predictable handling and composed ride quality. The AWD system adds peace of mind in varying weather conditions, giving this sedan an edge over many competitors. Overall, the 2017 Ford Fusion SE AWD 4-Door Sedan is a reliable, comfortable, and capable midsize car. It offers a well-rounded driving experience that suits daily errands, long highway journeys, and everything in between, with the added bonus of all-weather confidence thanks to its AWD system.

description: 2017 Honda Accord EX-L — overview and factory-standard features Powertrain and driving - 2.4L inline-4 engine, rated at 185 hp and 181 lb-ft of torque, paired with Honda’s continuously variable automatic transmission (CVT). The setup is tuned for a balance of everyday drivability and efficiency, with a focus on smooth power delivery in typical city and highway use. - Front-wheel drive and a suspension tuned for a comfortable, composed ride. Exterior - Body-colored exterior trim with tasteful chrome accents around the grille and window surrounds. - Multi-spoke alloy wheels and all-season tires (wheel size varies by market and optional packages). - Projector-style headlights and daytime running lights with integrated turn signals, body-color power mirrors (often heated on many EX-L models). - Integrated rear trunk release and a clean, understated sedan profile designed for aerodynamics and visibility. Interior and comfort - Leather-trimmed seating throughout the cabin, including supportive front seats designed for longer trips. - Heated front seats as standard on the EX-L. - Power-adjustable driver’s seat with lumbar support (multi-way adjustment) and manual or power adjustments for the front passenger seat depending on configuration. - Spacious seating for five with generous rear legroom and a fold-down 60/40 split rear seatback for added cargo flexibility. - Dual-zone automatic climate control to maintain separate comfort settings for driver and front passenger. - Leather-wrapped steering wheel with mounted controls for audio, phone, and cruise control. Convenience and keys - Smart entry with push-button ignition (Proximity keyless start) for keyless locking/unlocking and engine start. - Power windows and door locks with driver’s one-touch auto up/down function. - Remote trunk release and available remote engine start on some factory packages. Infotainment and connectivity - A centrally mounted display screen (Display Audio) that provides access to AM/FM audio, Bluetooth HandsFreeLink for phone calls, and Bluetooth Audio for streaming music. - USB and auxiliary inputs for device connectivity and charging, secondary USB port(s) available for passengers. - Steering-wheel audio and phone controls for convenient operation without taking hands off the wheel. - AM/FM/HD radio and premium audio system tuned for clear sound throughout the cabin (speaker count varies by configuration). - Many EX-L models were compatible with smartphone pairing for hands-free calling and media playback, navigation was available as an option or on higher packages. Safety and driver aids - Multi-airbag system including front, front-side and side-curtain airbags covering outboard seating positions. - Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) with Electronic Brake Distribution (EBD) and Brake Assist. - Vehicle Stability Assist (VSA) with traction control to help maintain control in slippery conditions. - Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). - Multi-angle rearview camera with dynamic guidelines for reversing and parking. - Honda offered additional driver-assist technologies (such as Collision Mitigation Braking System, Lane Keeping Assist, and Adaptive Cruise Control) through the Honda Sensing suite, which was optional or standard on certain model years/trims and packages, these systems were not universally standard on every 2017 EX-L. Practical features and storage - Ample interior storage including center console bin, cupholders, door pockets and front seatback pockets. - Fold-down rear seats increase cargo capacity for longer items and flexibility for daily needs. - Acoustic insulation and thoughtful interior ergonomics to reduce noise and improve long-distance comfort. Summary The 2017 Honda Accord EX-L is positioned as a premium mid-trim sedan that pairs the 2.4L 185-hp engine with a focus on comfort and convenience. description:
Thank you for choosing Butler Toyota of Jacksonville, this Super Black 2017 Nissan Altima 2.5 S is a great choice! Check out the following: No Accidents! City 27/Hwy 39 Power Driver Seat Package ($340 value)
  • 6-Way Power Driver's Seat
Comfort
  • Power reclining driver seat - Lean back. Gain some space between you and the wheel with power reclining driver seat. It lets you adjust the angle of the seatback at the touch of a button for added comfort while you're driving, or for a more comfortable rest while you're pulled over. Settle in, with power reclining driver seat.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

    Premier Sun and Wheel Package ($2,270 value)
    • Front and Rear Premium Floor Mats
    • Power Tilt Sliding Sunroof
    • P245/40R19 All Season Blackwall Tires
    • 19\' Aluminum Wheels
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

If you are searching for a dependable, comfortable, and fuel-efficient sedan that fits perfectly into daily Seattle driving, this 2017 Nissan Altima 2.5 SV in Brilliant Silver deserves your attention. With its sleek design, smooth ride, and impressive efficiency, this Altima is a smart choice for commuters, students, and anyone who values reliability with modern convenience. This recent arrival also comes with a Clean CARFAX and West Coast ownership history, offering added peace of mind from the moment you sit behind the wheel.
Under the hood, the proven 2.5L 4-cylinder engine paired with Nissans CVT with Xtronic delivers a smooth, responsive drive while achieving an outstanding 27 city and 39 highway MPG. Front-wheel drive and four-wheel independent suspension provide confident handling whether you are navigating city streets or heading out on a weekend getaway. This Altima is engineered to make every drive efficient, comfortable, and stress-free.
Step inside and you will appreciate a thoughtfully designed interior focused on comfort and convenience. The 2.5 SV trim adds premium touches like dual-zone automatic climate control, a power driver seat, leather-wrapped shift knob, and a front center armrest with storage. The AM/FM/CD/MP3 audio system with SiriusXM, steering wheel-mounted controls, and radio data system keep you connected and entertained on every trip. Bluetooth hands-free capability and remote keyless entry add everyday ease, while the split-folding rear seat offers flexibility for cargo when you need it.
Safety is a strong point for the Altima, with features designed to help protect you and your passengers. Electronic Stability Control, Traction Control, ABS brakes, Brake Assist, and a full suite of airbags work together to provide confident, controlled driving. Fully automatic headlights, fog lights, and a rear window defroster improve visibility in changing Northwest conditions, while the tire pressure monitoring system helps keep you informed on the road.

Experience driving excitement with this 2017 BMW 3 Series 330i — a sleek, performance-minded sedan located in McMinnville, OR. This model pairs dynamic performance with refined comfort, featuring leather seats that provide premium support and a sophisticated cabin ambiance. Stay connected and hands-free with built-in Bluetooth, making calls and streaming music effortless and safe. Automatic climate control keeps the interior temperature perfectly regulated for every passenger, enhancing comfort on long drives or quick commutes. Impeccable engineering meets everyday practicality in a car that handles like a sports sedan while remaining efficient and easy to live with. This 2017 BMW 330i comes competitively priced — offering the best price in the area — so you get exceptional value without compromise. Located in McMinnville, OR, this vehicle is ready for test drives and immediate enjoyment. If you want the ideal combination of luxury, performance, and technology in a compact executive sedan, this BMW 3 Series 330i is the smart choice. Reach out today to schedule a viewing and make this standout BMW yours before someone else does.

Equipment

The CVT transmission provides smooth, responsive power delivery, while the front-wheel-drive system offers confident handling and stability.

Inside, the Accord LX boasts a host of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of automatic climate control, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and a 160-Watt AM/FM audio system with CD player. The spacious cabin provides ample room for passengers and cargo, while the cloth upholstery and power accessories ensure a comfortable and well-equipped ride.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Accord LX offering a comprehensive suite of advanced features. Dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and Electronic Stability Control work together to provide you and your loved ones with peace of mind on every journey.

Whether you're commuting to the office or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2017 Honda Accord LX is the perfect companion. With its exceptional fuel efficiency, generous amenities, and proven reliability, it's a smart choice for discerning drivers like you.

We invite you to experience the Accord LX for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this impressive sedan can enhance your driving experience. With its unbeatable combination of style, performance, and value, the Accord LX is sure to exceed your expectations.

description:
Recent Arrival! Onyx Black Metallic 2017 Volvo S60 Inscription T5 Platinum FWD

Experience refined Scandinavian luxury with this recently arrived 2017 Volvo S60 Inscription T5 Platinum, now available at Autobahn Volvo in Fort Worth, TX. Finished in sophisticated Onyx Black Metallic, this S60 Inscription blends elegant design, advanced safety technology, and rewarding performance, making it an excellent choice for drivers seeking premium comfort at a competitive value. With 80,940 miles on the odometer, this Volvo has been driven responsibly and is ready for its next owner.

Under the hood, the Drive-E 2.0L turbocharged I4 engine delivers a smooth yet responsive driving experience, paired with an automatic transmission with Geartronic for confident and precise shifting. This front-wheel-drive sedan offers impressive efficiency, achieving an EPA-estimated 25 MPG city/37 MPG highway, making it an ideal luxury sedan for both commuting and longer road trips.

The Platinum trim represents the highest level of refinement in the S60 lineup and includes an exceptional array of high-value features. Notable highlights include Active Dual Xenon Headlights with Washers, Keyless Drive, Power Retractable Exterior Mirrors, a Grocery Bag Holder, and a Garage Door Transmitter with HomeLink. Comfort is enhanced with heated front seats and premium materials throughout the cabin.

This S60 is equipped with both the Convenience Package and Technology Package, providing advanced driver-assistance features designed to support confidence and peace of mind on the road. Safety highlights include Adaptive Cruise Control with Queue Assist, Collision Warning with Full Auto Brake, Pedestrian and Cyclist Detection with Auto Brake, Lane Keeping Aid, Driver Alert Control, Distance Alert, Road Sign Information, and Active High Beam Control. These intelligent systems showcase Volvo's long-standing leadership in automotive safety innovation.

Entertainment and connectivity are handled by the premium harman/kardon audio system, delivering rich sound quality for every drive. An auto-dimming rearview mirror further enhances visibility and driving comfort in varying conditions.

This Volvo S60 originally carried an MSRP of $43,230, offering outstanding luxury value today. At Autobahn Volvo, we use market-based pricing, so you can shop with confidence knowing this vehicle is priced competitively within current market conditions.

Our dealership proudly offers a wide variety of vehicles, including several pre-owned Volvo and Audi models, making it easy to find the right vehicle at a price you can feel good about. We also provide nationwide delivery, allowing you to purchase from virtually anywhere. For added peace of mind, extended service contracts are available-ask your sales associate for full details.

To make your shopping experience even more convenient, we offer virtual walkarounds, giving you the opportunity to see this vehicle up close from the comfort of your own home. A knowledgeable associate will guide you through the vehicle and answer any questions in real time.

This vehicle is located at our Volvo store in Fort Worth, TX and is available now.

Call (817) 390-3236 today to schedule a test drive, request your virtual walkaround, or learn more about available protection plans. Don't miss your chance to own this elegant and well-equipped Volvo S60 Inscription-luxury, safety, and value come together at Autobahn Volvo.
